REST server that performs translation from the given language based
on FreeDict TEI dictionary files. Please visit http://freedict.org/en/ to get more details.

For now only Dutch-English translation is supported. Other languages will be supported later.

Run: go run server.go

Request example:
http://localhost:9000/translate?text=%22Goedemorgen%20iedereen%22&from=NL&to=EN

Response:
<ServerResponse>
<Original>"Goedemorgen iedereen"</Original>
<Translated>goodmorning everyone</Translated>
<OriginalLang>NL</OriginalLang>
<TranslateToLang>EN</TranslateToLang>
</ServerResponse>

